    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i really dont want to deal with the whole doctor appointment thing again and wait weeks for a call back. i've already been feeling kinda shaky and lightheaded since i missed my dose this morning. if i just slowly taper off the sertraline over a week and start the st johns wort during that time, wouldnt that be a safe way to bridge the gap? i just want to feel better without all the chemicals.",
