      "content": "idk, the pharmacist is always busy and telehealth is expensive. i just feel like im overthinking the \"serotonin syndrome\" thing. i read on a forum that people do this transition all the time with just a few days gap. if i just take a very small amount of the sertraline for a few days then switch completely to the st johns wort, wouldn't that be fine? just tell me if there's a specific way to dose them so i don't mess up.",
